{"tid":1797922,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"今日濫捕證明左POPO暫時未有方法化解和理Shop","createTime":"2019-12-25T19:36:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-26T03:00:21.000Z","uid":95393,"like":29,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"08455ca653e63ab8245b66479f23fb57898803f6","tid":1797922,"uid":95393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T19:36:32.000Z","msg":"點解濫捕<br />\n因為佢哋分辦唔到今日真係shopping 定有行動既手足<br />\n但最後d 商場又真係早收<br />\n所以佢哋頭先係旺角鳩拉d 未返屋企既後生仔<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">想激刺勇武手足開花</span><br />\n呢度請大家保持冷靜唔好中伏<br />\n<br />\n暫時請大家keep 住和你shop<br />\n但有d 位我覺得可以改善<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">唔好black bloc</span><br />\n唔理你係想做嘢定純粹window shopping <br />\n你一bb 或者黑衫戴口罩基本上可以confirm 你係target<br />\n商場一封晒出口周圍又咁多便衣基本上好難走<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">唔好屌狗</span><br />\n商戶落閘其實就任務完成, 屌黎冇意思, 只會俾時間佢哋圍捕<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">有防暴出現就請準備撤退</span><br />\n一有green object 基本上都一定會鳩拉兼打人<br />\n呢個時候一定要最少同佢哋有段距離<br />\n有危險即走<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">商場半關都要走</span><br />\n都係安全問題, 完成任務請轉場<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">唔好期望POPO 會講道理</span><br />\n講道理就唔會濫捕鳩拉, 就算你係真shopping 都可以出事<br />\n見到POPO 就請留係安全嘅position <br />\n<br />\n我唔係勇武冇資格評判<br />\n但真係好想講, 如果我係POPO 我會最想見到一堆black bloc 人口罩人入商場, 封晒出入口慢慢捉<br />\n理大一戰已經證明左唔係人多就安全<br />\n下下百幾二百個手足被捕呢場運動就完架喇<br />\n請大家智取唔好硬碰<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">要不被捕 不流血 不送頭</span>"},{"pid":"13e522a6e05a6b7f72c49531e2a43ea6c9383f2b","tid":1797922,"uid":188685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T19:38:46.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">12.31 和你拖   <br />\n1.1維園見</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/URz5Cbv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FURz5Cbv.jpg&h=65a7904f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nthShbw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnthShbw.jpg&h=b187ac9f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Bv8RxKS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBv8RxKS.jpg&h=bf7fac51&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/12/26/032619_4639998b31741b81bff15a268ecdf66a.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F12%2F26%2F032619_4639998b31741b81bff15a268ecdf66a.jpeg&h=683fbec5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/12/26/032620_e6a6afab95e1b96c58635bc9ecff62d4.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F12%2F26%2F032620_e6a6afab95e1b96c58635bc9ecff62d4.jpeg&h=8bf36aa4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/12/26/032621_84b969a5799cd131bf0d8d77711f2a4c.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F12%2F26%2F032621_84b969a5799cd131bf0d8d77711f2a4c.jpeg&h=5c904a4b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f293bac1d640b4f187d04a9b73fb26e796e0d599","tid":1797922,"uid":264246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"13e522a6e05a6b7f72c49531e2a43ea6c9383f2b","tid":1797922,"uid":188685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T19:38:46.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">12.31 和你拖   <br />\n1.1維園見</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/URz5Cbv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FURz5Cbv.jpg&h=65a7904f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nthShbw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnthShbw.jpg&h=b187ac9f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Bv8RxKS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBv8RxKS.jpg&h=bf7fac51&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/12/26/032619_4639998b31741b81bff15a268ecdf66a.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F12%2F26%2F032619_4639998b31741b81bff15a268ecdf66a.jpeg&h=683fbec5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/12/26/032620_e6a6afab95e1b96c58635bc9ecff62d4.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F12%2F26%2F032620_e6a6afab95e1b96c58635bc9ecff62d4.jpeg&h=8bf36aa4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/12/26/032621_84b969a5799cd131bf0d8d77711f2a4c.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F12%2F26%2F032621_84b969a5799cd131bf0d8d77711f2a4c.jpeg&h=5c904a4b&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T19:41:20.000Z","msg":"屌唔屌狗同走唔走到真係2件事,咪吹淡風"},{"pid":"85109eaebbc733b9f9445d95bb31e0b1418b4e80","tid":1797922,"uid":95393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T19:43:31.000Z","msg":"其實和你shop 同和你suck 黎明行動性質一樣<br />\n合法又有成效<br />\n但和你suck 太遠又有禁制令<br />\n黎明手足好難keep 到好早起身<br />\n今次和你shop 成效未必好高但都係一個比起遊行或者開花安全好多嘅手段, 但相對都要人多先得<br />\n請大家都支持個活動"},{"pid":"2086ea219b578aa280b176fa01515ca6b897b954","tid":1797922,"uid":62841,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T19:47:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><ins>SHOP商場戰略檢討與重點</ins></strong></span> 幫手share<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><ins><strong>1) 12點好撤，再留係度攬炒指數低</strong></ins></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\">咁夜對政權既傷害係邊度? 個撚個都返鳩哂屋企訓教, 車又少。同玩平原戰 自殺有咩分別? 大家要記住個目標係乜野。街上又無其他路人幫你地cover, 過左12點又無車走。好似琴日MK咁, D人又話走唔撚到比狗包圍住。咁唔該你地今日咪撚再要呀寶出動</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><ins>2) 落閘就目標已達成, 可以轉場</ins></strong></span><br />\n商場落閘基本上都係因為D狗入撚哂黎, 咁達成目標 無需要再屌狗同戀戰<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><ins>3) 回馬槍，D狗走個時唔撚好再上前</ins></strong></span><br />\n尤其是商場入面，例如琴日ＹＯＨＯ已經比人回馬槍左起碼3-4次。每次都捉撚左2-3個。屌狗還屌狗, 你地係後面屌就爽, 企前面既街坊就中伏。唔好再做豬隊友<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><ins>4) 街坊被捕個時麻煩街坊咪撚係度嘈</ins></strong></span><br />\n琴日已經有幾次係因為街坊太嘈, 個街坊大聲叫都無人聽到佢講乜, 咁樣同害9自己友無分別。一陣無名無姓無資料, 係咪想人地被消失??"},{"pid":"fa03be96ee292a7c8d48908dc4cd50f395531274","tid":1797922,"uid":95393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f293bac1d640b4f187d04a9b73fb26e796e0d599","tid":1797922,"uid":264246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"13e522a6e05a6b7f72c49531e2a43ea6c9383f2b","tid":1797922,"uid":188685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T19:38:46.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">12.31 和你拖   <br />\n1.1維園見</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/URz5Cbv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FURz5Cbv.jpg&h=65a7904f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nthShbw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnthShbw.jpg&h=b187ac9f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Bv8RxKS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBv8RxKS.jpg&h=bf7fac51&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/12/26/032619_4639998b31741b81bff15a268ecdf66a.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F12%2F26%2F032619_4639998b31741b81bff15a268ecdf66a.jpeg&h=683fbec5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/12/26/032620_e6a6afab95e1b96c58635bc9ecff62d4.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F12%2F26%2F032620_e6a6afab95e1b96c58635bc9ecff62d4.jpeg&h=8bf36aa4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/12/26/032621_84b969a5799cd131bf0d8d77711f2a4c.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F12%2F26%2F032621_84b969a5799cd131bf0d8d77711f2a4c.jpeg&h=5c904a4b&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,